島（睇埋日落）-廣島<br />\nDay 3: 廣島-尾道/倉敷-大阪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係 <br />\nDay 1:大阪- 廣島 1400-1500到 去宮島 (黃昏) - 廣島<br />\nDay 2: 廣島-忠海-兔島-尾道-廣島<br />\nDay 3: 廣島市內 和平公園 紀念館etc. - 大阪<br />\n<br />\n有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5354f8a79baa632458f827a3df136255ec5fd8d8","tid":224852,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai_hiroshima/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Ftc%2Fticket%2Fpass%2Fkansai_hiroshima%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1azQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=17ae83ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai_hiroshima/</a><br />\n<br />\n關西廣島pass都唔係貴巴士好多 新幹線慳好多時間<br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 大阪-廣島市觀光 <br />\nDay 2: 廣島-(optional:岩國)-宮島（睇埋日落）-廣島<br />\nDay 3: 廣島-尾道/倉敷-大阪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係 <br />\nDay 1:大阪- 廣島 1400-1500到 去宮島 (黃昏) - 廣島<br />\nDay 2: 廣島-忠海-兔島-尾道-廣島<br />\nDay 3: 廣島市內 和平公園 紀念館etc. - 大阪<br />\n<br />\n有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nday1 太趕，廣島落宮島一個鐘車，神社好早收<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 坐新幹線一定無問題，又快又舒服"},{"pid":"69f06c6c9e6efab89452638d75b834e17d5f0534","tid":224852,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"btw, 你可以考慮下岡山，姬路等，唔駛咁趕"},{"pid":"00548a42fd23a16e0456de0ca6bc0b0971cd203f","tid":224852,"uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:29:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai_hiroshima/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Ftc%2Fticket%2Fpass%2Fkansai_hiroshima%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1azQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=17ae83ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai_hiroshima/</a><br />\n<br />\n關西廣島pass都唔係貴巴士好多 新幹線慳好多時間<br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 大阪-廣島市觀光 <br />\nDay 2: 廣島-(optional:岩國)-宮島（睇埋日落）-廣島<br />\nDay 3: 廣島-尾道/倉敷-大阪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係 <br />\nDay 1:大阪- 廣島 1400-1500到 去宮島 (黃昏) - 廣島<br />\nDay 2: 廣島-忠海-兔島-尾道-廣島<br />\nDay 3: 廣島市內 和平公園 紀念館etc. - 大阪<br />\n<br />\n有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nday1 太趕，廣島落宮島一個鐘車，神社好早收<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 坐新幹線一定無問題，又快又舒服</blockquote><br />\n咁我第一日可以早D既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同朋友食埋lunch就出發<br />\nanyway thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2068f5bc5cf91817396a825918800bb2f6960233","tid":224852,"uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw, 你可以考慮下岡山，姬路等，唔駛咁趕</blockquote><br />\n岡山有咩睇?<br />\n姬路好似得姬路城 但我對睇城池興趣不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e58f959cbe06656cb10b5477018c8370e9925c","tid":224852,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁chur 我三日最多都係京都大阪和歌山炸"},{"pid":"f6ec8642973dd016c4e11f22327d91567a0de62e","tid":224852,"uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:35:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁chur 我三日最多都係京都大阪和歌山炸</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似你仲chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}